OL,3,C'Get on' with fixing the 'broken
OL,4,Croads', Keir Starmer tells councils
OL,6,FThe government has urged councils to
OL,7,Ffix potholes, as ITV News' Ben Chapman
OL,8,Fexplains
OL,10,FSir Keir Starmer has urged councils to
OL,11,F"get on with the job" of fixing
OL,12,Fpothole-plagued roads, which he warned
OL,13,F"can risk lives and cost families
OL,14,Fhundreds if not thousands of pounds on
OL,15,Frepairs".
