OL,3,C'Get on' with fixing the 'broken
OL,4,Croads', Keir Starmer tells councils
OL,6,FThe prime minister made the comments
OL,7,Fas the Department for Transport (DfT)
OL,8,Fannounced how much each local
OL,9,Fauthority in England will receive to
OL,10,Fmaintain roads in the next financial
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FThe Treasury announced in the Budget
OL,14,Fin October that total local road
OL,15,Fmaintenance funding in 2025/26 will be
OL,16,Fnearly #1.6 billion, representing a
OL,17,F#500 million uplift compared with the
OL,18,Fprevious 12 months.
OL,20,FThe funding allocations include:
