OL,3,C'Get on' with fixing the 'broken
OL,4,Croads', Keir Starmer tells councils
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the AA found tackling the
OL,7,Fissue is a priority for 96% of
OL,8,Fmotorists.
OL,10,FThe DfT said it will make sure highway
OL,11,Fauthorities "spend the money wisely",
OL,12,Fcollect accurate data and deliver
OL,13,F"proactive maintenance" before
OL,14,Fpotholes start to form.
OL,16,FA quarter of the increased funding
OL,17,Fwill be held back until authorities
OL,18,Fhave "shown that they are delivering",
OL,19,Fthe DfT added.
