OL,3,C'Get on' with fixing the 'broken
OL,4,Croads', Keir Starmer tells councils
OL,6,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,7,Fexpressed confidence that the "really
OL,8,Fsignificant investment" will result in
OL,9,Fdrivers noticing an improvement in
OL,10,Froad conditions.
OL,12,F"This is massive," she said. "It's up
OL,13,Fto councils how they use the money.
OL,14,FThey can fill potholes, they can
OL,15,Fresurface roads, they can improve
OL,16,Fpavements, they can repair bridges."
OL,17,Fshe added
