OL,3,C'Get on' with fixing the 'broken
OL,4,Croads', Keir Starmer tells councils
OL,6,F"We will be asking councils to report
OL,7,Fback to us about how they spent that
OL,8,Fmoney. I'm confident that the public
OL,9,Fwill start to see an improvement in
OL,10,Fthe state of the roads."
OL,12,FSimon Williams, the lead spokesperson
OL,13,Ffor the RAC, stated that additional
OL,14,Fgovernment funding could be a "turning
OL,15,Fpoint" for addressing pothole issues
OL,16,Facross Britain
OL,18,FAA president Edmund King described the
OL,19,Ffunding as a "significant cash
OL,20,Finjection".
